---
// Demo section — renders a static terminal mock that mirrors the output spec
// in sphinx-agent/docs/DEMO-SCRIPT.md. When the real GIF is recorded (ScreenToGif
// or VHS → public/demo.gif), swap the <div class="terminal"> below for an <img>.
---

<section id="demo" class="demo">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-label">Demo</h2>
    <h3 class="section-title">One command. No API key required.</h3>
    <p class="caption">
      A real <code>npx mythos-agent quick</code> against a vulnerable fixture.
      Pattern scan runs in ~10&nbsp;ms, offline, no config.
    </p>

    <figure class="figure">
      <div
        class="terminal"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Terminal running npx mythos-agent quick. Five high-severity findings are surfaced in 10 milliseconds, with a suggested auto-fix command."
      >
        <div class="term-chrome" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="dot red"></span>
          <span class="dot yellow"></span>
          <span class="dot green"></span>
          <span class="term-title">bash — mythos-agent</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="term-body"><span class="dim"># find security bugs in your code</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">npx mythos-agent quick</span>

<span class="ok">✓</span> Scanned 47 files in <span class="accent">10 ms</span>

<span class="sev-crit">🔴 CRITICAL</span>  SQL Injection           <span class="muted">src/api/users.ts:42</span>
<span class="sev-crit">🔴 CRITICAL</span>  JWT None Algorithm      <span class="muted">src/auth/verify.ts:18</span>
<span class="sev-crit">🔴 CRITICAL</span>  Hardcoded DB Password   <span class="muted">src/db/connect.ts:7</span>
<span class="sev-high">🟠 HIGH</span>      Reflected XSS           <span class="muted">src/views/search.tsx:31</span>
<span class="sev-high">🟠 HIGH</span>      Reflected XSS           <span class="muted">src/views/profile.tsx:54</span>
<span class="muted">   …and 8 more</span>

<span class="accent">→ mythos-agent fix --severity critical --apply</span></pre>
      </div>
      <figcaption>
        Transcript: <code>npx mythos-agent quick</code> → scanned 47 files in 10 ms →
        5 findings visible with file:line pointers → auto-fix hint. 13 total findings.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .demo {
    padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .wrap {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .caption {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    max-width: 42rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
  .caption code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875em;
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .figure {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  figcaption {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-subtle);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  figcaption code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: var(--code-bg);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }

  .terminal {
    background: #0b0b0f;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a33;
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #fafafa;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px -20px var(--glow);
  }
  .term-chrome {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a33;
    background: #14141a;
  }
  .term-chrome .dot {
    width: 0.65rem;
    height: 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .term-chrome .dot.red {
    background: #ef4444;
  }
  .term-chrome .dot.yellow {
    background: #f59e0b;
  }
  .term-chrome .dot.green {
    background: #10b981;
  }
  .term-title {
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  .term-body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    white-space: pre;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .term-body .dim {
    color: #6b7280;
  }
  .term-body .prompt {
    color: #22d3ee;
  }
  .term-body .cmd {
    color: #fafafa;
  }
  .term-body .ok {
    color: #10b981;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .term-body .accent {
    color: #22d3ee;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .term-body .muted {
    color: #6b7280;
  }
  .term-body .sev-crit {
    color: #ef4444;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .term-body .sev-high {
    color: #fb923c;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
